  "detailed_description": "Milky Way is a mix of Tower Defense, RTS, Auto-Battler and Survivors genres. Visit planets in the Milky Way Galaxy and protect them against hordes of enemies.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >BUILD YOUR BASE</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2837330/extras/0abbff83d0a43e77076829634f9a2c90.poster.avif?t=1711739169\" width=750 height=306 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2837330/extras/0abbff83d0a43e77076829634f9a2c90.webm?t=1711739169\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2837330/extras/0abbff83d0a43e77076829634f9a2c90.mp4?t=1711739169\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Develop your economy: gather stone with mines and gold with furnaces.<br>Strengthen your defenses: use collected resources to build towers to fight off the enemies.<br>Towers are divided into two types: some of them summon units, while others attack enemies. Some of the summoned units are perfect in order to distract enemies against themselves and protect other towers. Remember that the good placement of the towers is the key to victory.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >USE SKILLS</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2837330/extras/9fd757db37ad21349b00393547a44259.poster.avif?t=1711739169\" width=750 height=380 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2837330/extras/9fd757db37ad21349b00393547a44259.webm?t=1711739169\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2837330/extras/9fd757db37ad21349b00393547a44259.mp4?t=1711739169\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Gather mana with pylons and spend it on powerfull skills. You can summon a giant meteor, shoot with orbital gun or unleash a starfall on your enemies. Use everything to win!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >SURVIVE!</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2837330/extras/d61d25f65ca056f67c13dcb13a8239c8.poster.avif?t=1711739169\" width=750 height=296 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2837330/extras/d61d25f65ca056f67c13dcb13a8239c8.webm?t=1711739169\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2837330/extras/d61d25f65ca056f67c13dcb13a8239c8.mp4?t=1711739169\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>There're over 40 types of enemies in the game, some of them have dangerous abilities. Can you survive against all of them?<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >FEATURES</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Dynamic and engaging gameplay<br></li><li> A variety of gameplay styles<br></li><li> 11 towers with their own abilities<br></li><li> 4 maps with unique atmosphere<br></li><li> Multitude of upgrades to choose from</li></ul><br>",
