s. You can summon a giant meteor, shoot with orbital gun or unleash a starfall on your enemies. Use everything to win!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >SURVIVE!</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2837330/extras/d61d25f65ca056f67c13dcb13a8239c8.poster.avif?t=1711739169\" width=750 height=296 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2837330/extras/d61d25f65ca056f67c13dcb13a8239c8.webm?t=1711739169\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2837330/extras/d61d25f65ca056f67c13dcb13a8239c8.mp4?t=1711739169\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>There're over 40 types of enemies in the game, some of them have dangerous abilities. Can you survive against all of them?<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >FEATURES</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Dynamic and engaging gameplay<br></li><li> A variety of gameplay styles<br></li><li> 11 towers with their own abilities<br></li><li> 4 maps with unique atmosphere<br></li><li> Multitude of upgrades to choose from</li></ul><br>",
